        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "50∴DEIIBC ABM $\\frac{A N}{A M}=\\frac{A D}{A B}=\\frac{D N}{B M}$ △ANE∽△AMC $\\frac{A D}{A D}=\\frac{A E}{A C}=\\frac{D E}{M C}$ 又∵AN=2NM \n$\\therefore\\frac{A N}{A M}=\\frac{2}{3}$ 故两组相似的相化人比设∴$S_{\\Delta A D O}=4k$ $\\frac{S_{\\Delta A D N}}{S_{\\Delta A B M}}=(\\frac{2}{3})^{2}=\\frac{4}{9},\\frac{S_{\\Delta A N E}}{S_{\\Delta A N C}}=(\\frac{2}{3})^{2}=\\frac{4}{9}$ <均为$\\fra{}{}$经$S_{\\Delta A M C}=9t$ $\\frac{S_{\\Delta A D N}}{S_{\\Delta A B M}}=(\\frac{2}{3})^{2}=\\frac{4}{9},\\frac{S_{\\Delta A N E}}{S_{\\Delta A N C}}=(\\frac{2}{3})^{2}=\\frac{4}{9}$ \n$S_{\\Delta A B C}=S_{\\Delta A B M}+S_{\\Delta A M C}=9k+90$ \n$S_{\\Delta D N M}=\\frac{1}{2}S_{\\Delta A D N}$ (等高不等底)\n\n$S_{\\Delta}m O E=\\frac{1}{2}S_{\\Delta}A N E\\sim\\frac{1}{10}E D$ \n$\\because S_{\\Delta D N M}=2k,S_{\\Delta M N E}=2t$ \n$S_{\\Delta M D E}=S_{\\Delta D M N}+S_{\\Delta M N E}=2k+2t\\cdot\\frac{S_{\\Delta D M E}}{S_{\\Delta A B C}}=\\frac{2k+2t}{9k+9t}=\\frac{2(k+t)}{9(k+t)}=\\frac{2}{9}.$ 6.在四边形ABCD中，AD∥BC，AB与CO不平行根据图中数据，若BA.CD延长后于点M，2△MBc的周长为\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            321,
